title: Sigur Ros - Takk (Complete Album - FLAC)
description:
This is the complete album "Takk" by Sigur Ros, including their most well-known and popular song "Hoppipolla".  The entire album was ripped from a Master Audio studio files (24bit/192KHz) and converted directly to 16bit FLAC, no steps in between, preserving the quality of the original master as much as possible without the massive file size of the original studio masters (188-355MB/ea).

Enjoy and please remember to seed!
